    <a id="add-an-individual-portal"></a>
    <section>
      <h3>1. Add an Individual Portal</h3>
        <p>You can add a portal by:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Submitting an issue on Github</li>
          <li>Using Data Explorer</li>
          <li>Submitting a pull request on GitHub</li>
        </ol>

        <h4>How to Submit a Portal as a Github Issue</h4>

        <p>Press the button below to get started. This will redirect your browser to a page that will create a new <a href="https://help.github.com/articles/creating-an-issue/">Github issue</a> for review.</p>

        <p><a href="https://github.com/okfn/dataportals.org/issues/new" class="btn btn-primary" role="button">Add a Portal</a></p>

        <h5>What happens next?</h5>
        <p>The issue will be reviewed by and incorporated into DataPortals.org pending no data errors.</p>

